{"error":false,"data":"<section\r\n    class=\"flat-section-v2 flat-testimonial-v2 wow fadeInUpSmall\"\r\n    data-wow-delay=\".2s\"\r\n    data-wow-duration=\"2000ms\"\r\n    style=\"\"\r\n>\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        \r\n        <div\r\n            class=\"swiper tf-sw-testimonial\"\r\n            data-preview-lg=\"3\"\r\n            data-preview-md=\"2\"\r\n            data-preview-sm=\"2\"\r\n            data-space=\"30\"\r\n            data-autoplay=\"true\"\r\ndata-autoplay-speed=\"5000\"\r\ndata-loop=\"true\"\r\n\r\n        >\r\n            <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                        <div class=\"box-tes-item style-1\">\r\n                         <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/search?sca_esv=f9a3c13abd781ae7&sxsrf=ANbL-n7-kDu7-cWD7Inykzfg9UCVNzbd1A:1776804112765&si=AL3DRZEsmMGCryMMFSHJ3StBhOdZ2-6yYkXd_doETEE1OR-qOfvoulo1K3CdIC5M45JUCC4r873m2qwN7EicjGCMgYWtNzBTKNl8PkUaJZYYaU6q_EC5LNKLYfGq1WitFm3vQOmt5TFOzgO3dLn3bfm3a6YNV2Pe8g%3D%3D&q=Serik+Realty+Inc.+Reviews&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiV_OeP5_-TAxWkmSsGHSvSEY8Q0bkNegQIRRAH&biw=1482&bih=704&dpr=1.25\" target=\"_blank\"> <ul class=\"list-star\">\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n    <p class=\"note body-1\">\r\n        <p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(77,81,86);\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\">I sold and bought two houses using Sadaquat. Also used his services for sourcing tenants twice. He is very professional, and provides good advice, with a customer centric focus. He also has authentic and verified recommendations of lawyers, brokers and contractors who are at the same level as himself.\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n    <\/p>\r\n<div class=\"box-avt d-flex align-items-center gap-12\">\r\n    <div class=\"avatar avt-60 round\">\r\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/serik.ca\/storage\/unnamed-4.png\" data-bb-lazy=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Desmond Mahadeo\">\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"info\">\r\n        <div class=\"h7 fw-7\">Desmond Mahadeo<\/div>\r\n        <p class=\"text-variant-1 mt-4\">Happy Home Seeker<\/p>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/a>  \r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                        <div class=\"box-tes-item style-1\">\r\n                         <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/search?sca_esv=f9a3c13abd781ae7&sxsrf=ANbL-n7-kDu7-cWD7Inykzfg9UCVNzbd1A:1776804112765&si=AL3DRZEsmMGCryMMFSHJ3StBhOdZ2-6yYkXd_doETEE1OR-qOfvoulo1K3CdIC5M45JUCC4r873m2qwN7EicjGCMgYWtNzBTKNl8PkUaJZYYaU6q_EC5LNKLYfGq1WitFm3vQOmt5TFOzgO3dLn3bfm3a6YNV2Pe8g%3D%3D&q=Serik+Realty+Inc.+Reviews&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiV_OeP5_-TAxWkmSsGHSvSEY8Q0bkNegQIRRAH&biw=1482&bih=704&dpr=1.25\" target=\"_blank\"> <ul class=\"list-star\">\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n    <p class=\"note body-1\">\r\n        <p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(77,81,86);\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;word-spacing:0px;\">I had an excellent experience working with Gary Sodhi. He is incredibly thorough, pays close attention to every detail, and communicates clearly at every step of the process. He made everything easy to understand and was always available to answer questions.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n    <\/p>\r\n<div class=\"box-avt d-flex align-items-center gap-12\">\r\n    <div class=\"avatar avt-60 round\">\r\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/serik.ca\/storage\/unnamed-3.png\" data-bb-lazy=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Gundeep Sidhu_tung\">\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"info\">\r\n        <div class=\"h7 fw-7\">Gundeep Sidhu_tung<\/div>\r\n        <p class=\"text-variant-1 mt-4\">Property Investor<\/p>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/a>  \r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                        <div class=\"box-tes-item style-1\">\r\n                         <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/search?sca_esv=f9a3c13abd781ae7&sxsrf=ANbL-n7-kDu7-cWD7Inykzfg9UCVNzbd1A:1776804112765&si=AL3DRZEsmMGCryMMFSHJ3StBhOdZ2-6yYkXd_doETEE1OR-qOfvoulo1K3CdIC5M45JUCC4r873m2qwN7EicjGCMgYWtNzBTKNl8PkUaJZYYaU6q_EC5LNKLYfGq1WitFm3vQOmt5TFOzgO3dLn3bfm3a6YNV2Pe8g%3D%3D&q=Serik+Realty+Inc.+Reviews&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiV_OeP5_-TAxWkmSsGHSvSEY8Q0bkNegQIRRAH&biw=1482&bih=704&dpr=1.25\" target=\"_blank\"> <ul class=\"list-star\">\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n    <p class=\"note body-1\">\r\n        <p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(77,81,86);\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;\">This realtor company exceeded our expectations. They were patient, honest, and extremely thorough throughout the process. No pressure, no confusion, just clear guidance and solid advice. It\u2019s rare to find professionals who are both skilled and genuinely caring, but this team delivered on both.\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n    <\/p>\r\n<div class=\"box-avt d-flex align-items-center gap-12\">\r\n    <div class=\"avatar avt-60 round\">\r\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/serik.ca\/storage\/unnamed-2.png\" data-bb-lazy=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Ajay Pal Singh Sandhu\">\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"info\">\r\n        <div class=\"h7 fw-7\">Ajay Pal Singh Sandhu<\/div>\r\n        <p class=\"text-variant-1 mt-4\">Delighted Home Seller<\/p>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/a>  \r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                        <div class=\"box-tes-item style-1\">\r\n                         <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/search?sca_esv=f9a3c13abd781ae7&sxsrf=ANbL-n7-kDu7-cWD7Inykzfg9UCVNzbd1A:1776804112765&si=AL3DRZEsmMGCryMMFSHJ3StBhOdZ2-6yYkXd_doETEE1OR-qOfvoulo1K3CdIC5M45JUCC4r873m2qwN7EicjGCMgYWtNzBTKNl8PkUaJZYYaU6q_EC5LNKLYfGq1WitFm3vQOmt5TFOzgO3dLn3bfm3a6YNV2Pe8g%3D%3D&q=Serik+Realty+Inc.+Reviews&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiV_OeP5_-TAxWkmSsGHSvSEY8Q0bkNegQIRRAH&biw=1482&bih=704&dpr=1.25\" target=\"_blank\"> <ul class=\"list-star\">\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n    <li class=\"icon icon-star\"><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n    <p class=\"note body-1\">\r\n        <p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(77,81,86);\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;\">I had a pleasure to work with Gary Sodhi on multiple projects. He is an excellent real estate agent who truly goes beyond just buying and selling property. He consistently bring valuable business ideas, investment opportunities, and insights into small business planning, financial planning, and trade investments.<\/span> \u00a0<\/span><\/p>\r\n    <\/p>\r\n<div class=\"box-avt d-flex align-items-center gap-12\">\r\n    <div class=\"avatar avt-60 round\">\r\n        <img src=\"https:\/\/serik.ca\/storage\/unnamed-1.png\" data-bb-lazy=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Vikram Malhotra\">\r\n    <\/div>\r\n    <div class=\"info\">\r\n        <div class=\"h7 fw-7\">Vikram Malhotra<\/div>\r\n        <p class=\"text-variant-1 mt-4\">Happy New Homeowner<\/p>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/a>  \r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"sw-pagination sw-pagination-testimonial\"><\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<script>\r\nconst testimonialSwiper = new Swiper('.tf-sw-testimonial', {\r\n    slidesPerView: 1,\r\n    spaceBetween: 30,\r\n    loop: true,\r\n    autoplay: {\r\n        delay: 3000,\r\n        disableOnInteraction: false,\r\n    },\r\n});\r\n    const swiperEl = document.querySelector('.tf-sw-testimonial');\r\n\r\nif (swiperEl) {\r\n    swiperEl.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {\r\n        testimonialSwiper.autoplay.stop();\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    swiperEl.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {\r\n        testimonialSwiper.autoplay.start();\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n<\/script>\r\n","message":null}